Kyrie, rex immensae pietatis, laudes exaudi famulantum devote tibi, eleyson.

Kyrie, universae creaturae potens creator, nobis semper assis protector, eleyson.

Kyrie, spirans multifarie vatibus loquenda prophetice secreta caelestis gloriae tua dona nobis infunde, eleyson.
